# API Design Template

## RESTful Endpoints
- Use appropriate HTTP methods (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE)
- Follow consistent URL patterns: `/api/v1/resources`
- Return appropriate status codes

## Data Flow
- Controllers receive data, don't create it
- Business logic in pure functions
- Database actions at service layer edges

## Error Handling
- Return structured error responses
- Log errors but don't mix logging with business logic
- Validate input data before processing
